Interface ExpressionService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardExpressionService

    @RemoteInterface
public interface ExpressionService
    A service to create/modify Expressionable and wt.option.ExpressionMemberLink objects.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
